Troubleshooting
Issue: Tasks not executing

Check if engine.start() was called
Verify workers are created correctly
Ensure task queue is not empty
Issue: RuntimeError about event loop

Use asyncio.run() for top-level execution
Don't mix sync and async code incorrectly
Issue: Tasks hanging indefinitely

Add timeout to task execution
Check for blocking operations in async functions
Use await for all async calls
Issue: Import errors

Verify virtual environment is activated
Reinstall packages: pip install aiohttp aiofiles
